Incoming livestream: It's a threat modeling framework.

97
00:22:55.498 --> 00:23:04.268
Incoming livestream: Maestro. Sorry, can you repeat that one more time? I'm wondering, like, if you took into account, or are thinking about Maestro threat modeling framework into account?

98
00:23:04.748 --> 00:23:07.218
Incoming livestream: So the Maestro threat modeling framework.

99
00:23:07.488 --> 00:23:24.258
Incoming livestream: I think that could be something we build out in the future. I think for now, just building on our existing processes, most of it has been in the MITRE format, but I think that format could go well based on, you know, what sort of, like, risk and security views we're seeing, where it could be more applicable.

